ottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">=
 the 30+%</a> it was earning in the boom years before the 2008 crisis.</p><=
p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The leading focus now is Goldman=E2=80=99s=C2=
=A0asset and wealth management business, the classic source of stable recur=
ring revenues for investment banks; the first slide in <a href=3D"https://l=
ink.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30698374.259422/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ29sZG=
1hbnNhY2hzLmNvbS9pbnZlc3Rvci1yZWxhdGlvbnMvaW52ZXN0b3ItZGF5LTIwMjMvbXVsdGltZ=
WRpYS9wcmVzZW50YXRpb25zL3BkZnMvYXNzZXQtYW5kLXdlYWx0aC1tYW5hZ2VtZW50LW1uLnBk=
