temscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none =
!important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-=
bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> that segment=E2=80=99s prese=
ntation</a> is titled =E2=80=9CLeading Asset and Wealth Management Platform=
 Delivering Durable Revenues and Earnings Growth.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=9CIncreas=
ing Fee-Based Revenues Will Create More Durable Earnings as We Navigate Var=
ious Market Cycles=E2=80=9D is the headline of another slide. =E2=80=9CThis=
 unit is the make-or-break path to getting a higher multiple,=E2=80=9D UBS =
Group AG banking analyst Brennan Hawken <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomb=
ergbusiness.com/click/30698374.259422/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZ=
XdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDItMjYvZ29sZG1hbi10dXJucy10by1tYWtlLW9yLWJyZWFrLXVu=
